::KitKat/DarkMouse::

KitKat::
She got hit in the shoulder and the leg.  She kept up a steady stream 
of lazar shots at Adrax.

DarkMouse::
She made it to a side hatch and opened it with the skill of a good 
lock pick. She crawled inside and scurried up the vent shaft 
stopped.  She sniffed around and went down a side vent.  She didn't 
bring her scanner s she had to use her nose.  She followed the scent 
of the other Preds, mainly Rampage through the vent.  She crawled 
down another side vent and found the bridge.  She looked through the 
vent and saw the main computer.  

(I don't know if anyone is on the bridge of the ship or not so let me 
know)
